      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know it's not \"ideal\" but i've heard people say a tiny bit of alcohol makes the meds work way better and helps them stay asleep. i don't drink that much, just like one glass of wine a week. is it really that dangerous if it's just a small amount to help the diazepam do its job? wouldn't the effect just be slightly stronger?",
